    "Management": {
      "text": "If xrays are\npositive\n(when indicated)\nTreat underlying condition\nIf xrays are\nnegative\nor not indicated\nOttawa knee rules\nDo full knee exam to check for ligamentous/meniscal instability:\nNegative exam → RICE\nPositive exam or unable to evaluate secondary to pain/swelling → knee brace + RICE",
